Line19.BAB4F: Walking these halls, I feel the weight of their sacrifice.
Line17.BAB4F: All that I can offer them is song and ceremony, but it never seems enough.
Line1.BAB4F: To bury so many of my brothers and sisters...their faces I cannot unsee.
Line3.BAB4F: Those I mentored, and those who mentored me in kind, are now forgotten.
